stability equations for conical shells ..Akempner,j..Bj. ae. scs. 25, 1958, 137..Wstability equations for conical shells .  the author rewrites v. s. vlasov's equations for (linear)stability theory of shells (prikl. mat. meh. 8(1944),109-placements .  the result is a single eighth-order equationfor normal deflection, and two fourth-order equationsrelating the displacement components in the shell middlesurface to the normal displacement .